data.description:
Welcome to the epitome of luxurious living at 2846 Trent Ct, Grand Prairie, TX. This meticulously crafted residence offers a perfect blend of sophistication and comfort, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a premium living experience.

Property Features:
3 Bedrooms
2 Bathrooms
Office Space
Cozy Fireplace
Serene Backyard Retreat

 Easy Access to Hwy 360 & I-20
 Minutes away from Joe Pool Lake
 Proximity to Shopping & Restaurants

The property's strategic location ensures easy access to major highways, making commuting a breeze. Joe Pool Lake, just minutes away, provides a picturesque escape, while a plethora of shopping and dining options cater to every lifestyle.
Don't miss the opportunity to call 2846 Trent Ct your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of modern living in a prime Grand Prairie location. Immerse yourself in luxury, convenience, and the allure of this exceptional property.
